FBIS4-55089 "dreeu090_b_94005" FBIS-EEU-94-090 Daily Report 9 May 1994 BULGARIA Internal Security Units Formed at Ministries Internal Security Units Formed at Ministries AU0905160294 Sofia Khorizont Radio Network in Bulgarian 1500 GMT 9 May 94 AU0905160294 Sofia Khorizont Radio Network Bulgarian BFN [Text] According to a government decision, units in charge of security and guarding facts, information, and objects that represent state security have been formed at the Council of Ministers, certain ministries, enterprises in the military-industrial complex, industrial plants, and representations across the border. The Ministry of Internal Affairs is responsible for the payroll and wages of these units' personnel. The employees will be officers of the National Security Service and the regional services.
